descriptionHtml:
Luba SkyWings Armor, will not replace parts (use his own slot) set  v1.2.5

In mod;
Morpho Bleu Wings
Monarch Wings
Lunar Moth Wings
Luba Blue Tunic
Demon Wings
DragonFly Wings


New in v1.2.5
Demon Wings map and crash fix
DragonFly Wings added


Install:
Extract in you skyrim main folder and make sure LubaSkyWings.esp is checked in the DATA section of your Skyrim Launcher. 


Ingame:
can be forge under misc section or Type in console: 
help morpho
help monarch
help lunar
help luba
help demon
player.additem




Contenu du mod;
Morpho Bleu Wings
Monarch Wings
Lunar Moth Wings
Luba Tunic Bleu
Demon Wings
Dragonfly wings

Nouveau v1.2.5
Demon Wings map and crash fix
Dragonfly  wings ajouté

Installer:
Extraire dans votre dossier Skyrim principal et assurez-vous LubaSkyWings.esp est cochée dans la section DATA de votre lanceur Skyrim.

Dans le jeu:
peut être forgé




Credit: Matthieu Pinsonneault
author: Matthieu Pinsonneault
